Project Modules

This project has declared the following modules:

Name Description
Apache Juneau Core Base toolkit for serializers, parsers, and bean contexts.
Apache Juneau Client REST client API.
Apache Juneau Server REST servlet API
Apache Juneau Microservice API for creating standalone executable jars that can be used to start lightweight configurable REST interfaces.
Apache Juneau Samples Sample code packaged as a microservice.
Apache Juneau Server Test Tests for Juneau Client and Server.
Apache Juneau Distribution Location to find fully build Juneau distributions.
